      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical R2023R1 used under vendor-issued QA certification; FDA in-house FEA code verified against NAFEMS benchmarks; DePuy Synthes solver subject to 21 CFR Part 11-compliant change-control procedures. Gradation 2 requires documented QA plan with periodic re-verification — all three codes satisfy this threshold.",
