      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification at Gradation 2 requires comparison against analytical solutions or established benchmarks for the relevant physics (large-displacement elasto-plastic beam bending). Benchmark suite covers cantilever beam plasticity and contact patch tests consistent with NAFEMS LE1 and NAFEMS NL2.",
      "rationale": "Patch tests and benchmark comparisons against NAFEMS LE1 and NL2 problems confirm correct implementation of elasto-plastic constitutive response and contact algorithms in all three codes. Errors below 1% in all benchmark QoIs."
