      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "rationale": "Testing performed under a single ASTM F1717 load configuration (compression-bending at 5 mm/min crosshead rate, ambient temperature). Only one test condition evaluated; multi-condition coverage required for Gradation 3 was not achieved. This factor is below the required level and represents a known gap in the validation evidence."
