      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Gradation 3 output comparison requires a quantitative metric accounting for both model error and experimental uncertainty. The E/uval metric (ASME V&V 40 Eq. 6) with threshold E/uval < 1.96 (95% confidence) applied to all three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm displacement). Additionally, percentage difference |QoI_FEA - QoI_mean_exp| / QoI_mean_exp < 10% required for each QoI.",
      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (0.81), yield force (1.12), and force at 40 mm (0.94). All values below 1.96 threshold. Percentage differences: stiffness 3.2%, yield force 5.7%, 40 mm force 4.1% — all within 10% bound. Output comparison factor satisfied at Gradation 3."
    },
