    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The one deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved Gradation 2 vs. required Gradation 3) is mitigated by the strong output comparison results (all E/uval < 1.96) and the physical consistency of the single validated condition with the intended use. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for this Class II device application.",
